The International University of Islamic Sciences seeks to combine knowledge and virtue based on faith and wisdom, so that it is a modern, comprehensive and pioneering Islamic university in its methodology and study plans to be distinguished as one of the most prestigious universities at the Arab, regional, Islamic and international levels. The university aims to provide the Arab and Islamic worlds with specialists capable of highlighting the bright image of Islam and Muslims in everything related to faith, Sharia, science, thought, civilization, arts and Islamic architecture, as a contribution to the Islamic civilizational project.
